			<div class="description col six">
				<br />
				<p><a href="../../">tweet-a-fleur</a></p>
				<p><em>2010</em></p>
				<p><em class="background">&ndash; A physical flower that embodies the happiness quotient of the world.</em></p>
				<br />
				<p>tweet-a-fleur is a real physical flower that sits on your desk. The flower senses the happiness quotient of the world by affectively analyzing real-time public twitter feeds. Based on the happy / sad state of the world - the flower physically blooms / droops.</p>

<p><br /></p>

<p><b>role:</b> Conceptualization, Hardware and Software Development.</p>

<p><b>skills:</b> Arduino, Shape-memory alloy, Processing, EmoTweet-core, Twitter API.</p>

				<br />
